### Code Maintainability

**File Size Limits:**
- **Target:** 300-500 lines per module
- **Warning:** >600 lines - consider splitting
- **Critical:** >800 lines - must refactor

When splitting files, organize by responsibility:
```
models/
├── user.py              # Re-exports for compatibility
├── user_crud.py         # Create, read, update, delete
├── user_queries.py      # Listing, filtering
└── user_utils.py        # Utilities
```

